<br>
Runed Circlet 4 Wis...200-250p<br>
6 Wisdom Rings...around 350p a pair depending on the chanter<br>
Plat Ruby Veil 7 str/wis...450-500p<br>
Gatorscale Leggings 4 Wis...500-600p <br>
Chared Guardian Shield 9 Wis...350-500p<br>
<br>
That will give u a nice addition of wisdom and you should have some cash left to buy spells.  Also might want to get a decent magic 1 HB like a Enamelled Black Mace pretty good and cheap now around 125-200p.  Also if you are low level you might want to go with moonstone rings around 150p a pair at the most.  Im using moonstones now because the extra 60 mana is nice and goes good with the 50 mana on my Ice cream cone.  But im only lvl 13 so I think the mana is better than wisdom at low levels. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.showPrevMessage?topicID=3245.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.showNextMessage?topicID=3245.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3245.topic&index=2><img src=http://dev.thedruidsgrove.org/images/forum/addreplya.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.emailToFriend?topicID=3245.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.threadControl?topicID=3245.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/gfx/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=3245.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=3245.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of